description: LibriVox recording of Christmas Roses, by Lizzie Lawson and Robert Ellice Mack. Read by Charlotte Duckett. A beautiful collection of pretty little poems. (Summary by Charlotte Duckett) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
